    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Nondestructive technique of activation analysis induced by neutrons. The prompt gamma rays immediately emitted by the sample are measured with a gamma ray spectrometer, allowing the identification of a wide variety of neutron-capturing elements simultaneously.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
